element.name: Millbank by Windsockers, Multi-cache (1/1)

center.p: The Millbank is a ruined 13th century windmill in the village of Rush

long-description.p: To find the cache you will need to visit a couple of locations to collect some information in order to discover the final location

At the above coordinates count the number of Windows call this Number A
Also count the number of gated doorways call this number call this Number B
Go to N53 31.334 W6 06.143and count the number of eyes call this Number C
Go to N53 31.330 W6 06.066 and note the three digit number call this Number D E F
The cache can be found at N 53 3D (E-B)FD W 006 0(C+A)(C-B)(E-C)F
Please re-hide the cache with care to prevent muggles from discovering its location
